summary: Lavander house is located near river between Riverwood and Whiterun. It\'s main features are huge rooms based on combination of Whiterun interior architecture with addition of great backyard world behind the house.
descriptionHtml:
House can be found next to river between Whiterun and Riverwood. Main version needs Dawnguard and Hearthfire plugins but there is also optional version without those requirements. Fully navmeshed.

Lavander house features:
-lots of containers
-bookshelves(for 544books)
-10 mannequins
-lots of weapon racks
-shrines
-herb garden with critters
-alchemy and enchanting workbenches
-cooking pots,oven and butter churn

Backyard features:
-lots of waterfalls,creeks and lakes with mostly fogy and rainy climate
-weapon forge(sky forge), smelter, tanning rack, etc..
-garden(again) +25plantable soil mounds
-beehives, critters, grain mill and fish hatchery
-domestic animals:cows, goats, chickens(and few deers)
-doomstones
-archery targets
-ore veins
author: PolarAenima
